{"tid":1590581,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"明明11月24號就係選舉，點解冇人提？","createTime":"2019-09-23T19:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T00:54:20.000Z","uid":260256,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a31032be4a6e2157b96e92ec4a2bb3c08b272f","tid":1590581,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:46:50.000Z","msg":"唔係割蓆，但<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明明區議會個選舉就係喺11月24日</span></span>，點解冇人提過？<br />\n大家文宣講之後搞咩講之後搞咩，十點咆哮十點咆哮，但點解唔可以留意返區議會？我哋要由區議會開始攞返系統內嘅話語權。<br />\n我知道大家自從16年立法會大選都好灰，睇住自己選入去嘅人比人DQ彈返出嚟，自己嘅意見同聲音硬生生比人鎖咗喺體制外面，谷到所有嘢都只係能夠上街。<br />\n到今日時代革命，香港人再一次醒覺，大家都落咗力去自己老豆老母自己救，del台嘅del台，和你塞嘅塞，簽聯署嘅聯署&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n無論革命成功與否，真係真係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家都要入番去體制入面</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我哋始終都要有兩手準備。"},{"pid":"5df682503eecdbaa8aea2d3a9ad162e569ae2aee","tid":1590581,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"0a02ee4384855ec5d5ada751dd1e2df3d3d5b976","tid":1590581,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:47:36.000Z","msg":"自推1-10"},{"pid":"56eb8044b4ed0352ae24c8360f032b3f1b356af0","tid":1590581,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:47:52.000Z","msg":"自推2-10"},{"pid":"49a6bdad93f9d63223b78cc33ada0456d26986e2","tid":1590581,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:53:20.000Z","msg":"自推3-10"},{"pid":"c9710dfa55f3e72364161a57bb03b7bd2fc7d787","tid":1590581,"uid":260256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T19:53:52.000Z","msg":"自推4-10"},